title: Volleyball Roundup: Generals win at home
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Generals win at home 11:08 p.m. EDT September 29, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Ridgewood 3, Hiland 0 
The Generals (11-2, 9-0) won at home Tuesday in three sets over Hiland 25-17, 25-6 and 25-14. Laura Crawford led Ridgewood with 15 kills, 15 digs, 6 blocks and 2 aces; Allie Dobson had 7 kills and 5 blocks, Eliza Haynes had 13 assists, 7 digs and 4 kills, Morgan McDorman had 10 digs and Sydney Zinkon had 11 assists, 7 digs and served an ace.
